						<div class="postbody">VSync should just be a bit going from low to high like on the NES. Yes I know that all kinds of programs might wait for it to go high and then all want a piece of the action at the same time but it would still be a nice feature especially if you could via the Windows API change which program(s) get the highest priority.</div>

					
